@startuml class_diagram_index
title Class Diagram Index

class "Domain Model" as Domain
class "Backend Services" as Backend
class "API DTO Contracts" as Api
class "WebSocket Events" as Ws

Domain --> Backend : used by
Api --> Backend : mapped by controllers
Ws --> Backend : published by services

note right of Domain
  Render individual modules from diagrams/.
  Each module is standalone PlantUML.
end note

@enduml
